.Dd April 23, 2026
.Dt MAT_VARWRITEINFO 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Mat_VarWriteInfo
.Nd Deprecated variable-write helper that is no longer supported.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Fd #include <matio.h>
.Ft int
.Fo Mat_VarWriteInfo
.Fa "const mat_t *mat"
.Fa "matvar_t *matvar"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn Mat_VarWriteInfo
function remains in the public API for compatibility, but current matio
versions do not support it.
Calls fail and emit a diagnostic directing callers to
.Fn Mat_VarWrite
or, for MAT 7.3 files, to
.Fn Mat_VarWriteAppend .
.Sh DEPRECATED
This function is deprecated since version 1.5.14.
Use \fBMat_VarWrite\fP or, for MAT 7.3 files, \fBMat_VarWriteAppend\fP instead.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The function returns
.Dv MATIO_E_OPERATION_NOT_SUPPORTED .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr Mat_VarWrite 3 ,
.Xr Mat_VarWriteAppend 3 ,
.Xr Mat_VarWriteData 3